                </me>.
                We integrate first with respect to <m>y</m>:
                <md>
                  <mrow>\int_{x=0}^{x=1}  \int_{y=x^2}^{y=x} xy \, dy  \, dx \amp = \int_{x=0}^{x=1} \frac{1}{2}xy^2 \mid_{y=x^2}^{y=x}  \, dx</mrow>
